org.apache.solr.update.processor

Class CdcrUpdateProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.solr.update.processor.UpdateRequestProcessor
      • org.apache.solr.update.processor.DistributedUpdateProcessor
        • org.apache.solr.update.processor.CdcrUpdateProcessor

  • public class CdcrUpdateProcessor
extends DistributedUpdateProcessor

    Extends DistributedUpdateProcessor to force peer sync logic for every updates. This ensures that the version parameter sent by the source cluster is kept by the target cluster.
